# This package is built and run inside Linux (WSL2 / ROS 2). Executable
# Python scripts MUST keep LF line endings, or their `#!/usr/bin/env python3`
# shebang becomes `python3\r` on checkout and the node dies with exit 127.
# Force LF for all text we care about regardless of the host git autocrlf setting.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.py text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf
*.world text eol=lf
*.sdf text eol=lf
*.launch.py text eol=lf
